  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1331510/extras/44d8fd68c46424b4eb4761752351d472.avif?t=1773991730\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1331510/extras/e358a313ad827fc994daac4df310de49.webp?t=1773991730\" width=600 height=35 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Next-Gen of VR Sword-Fighting</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle Talent is a <strong>challenging physics-based roguelite sword-fighting </strong>game, you can create your own fighting style and experience unparalleled gameplay in a mega seamless procedural dungeon. With over 80 enemy variants, 100 weapons, and 60 perks, the possibilities are endless.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join forces with your friends to take down enemies! Experience rich <strong>multiplayer</strong> interactions and create powerful combos!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1331510/extras/53ced430fa817b3f7b7440cebd77a84a.poster.avif?t=1773991730\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1331510/extras/53ced430fa817b3f7b7440cebd77a84a.webm?t=1773991730\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1331510/extras/53ced430fa817b3f7b7440cebd77a84a.mp4?t=1773991730\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience thrilling physical combat with <strong>spell, melee, and ranged attacks</strong>. Beware, target the boss! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1331510/extras/870898407c1746007842a7429119c2e3.poster.avif?t=1773991730\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1331510/extras/870898407c1746007842a7429119c2e3.webm?t=1773991730\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1331510/extras/870898407c1746007842a7429119c2e3.mp4?t=1773991730\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your talent points in <strong>Roguelike levels </strong>and unlock unexpected treasure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1331510/extras/75488a7a358d0b915b06385cdfee4fa3.poster.avif?t=1773991730\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1331510/extras/75488a7a358d0b915b06385cdfee4fa3.webm?t=1773991730\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1331510/extras/75488a7a358d0b915b06385cdfee4fa3.mp4?t=1773991730\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore <strong>Sandbox Mode</strong> to experiment with <strong>2000+ mods</strong> and Scene Editor feature.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1331510/extras/dc82e205c1b1f1ddaae3aa415ffaf458.poster.avif?t=1773991730\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1331510/extras/dc82e205c1b1f1ddaae3aa415ffaf458.webm?t=1773991730\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1331510/extras/dc82e205c1b1f1ddaae3aa415ffaf458.mp4?t=1773991730\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 game modes: Adventure, Challenge, Sandbox,  Multiplayer Mode (PvE & PvP)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Supports multiplayer mode for 2-6 players and includes a built-in voice chat </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Built-in scripted mod menu with 2000+ mods, enhance your gaming experience</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thrill of hack-and-slash with realistic physics interactions.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Variety of enemies and bosses, over 80 enemy variants with different moveset</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plenty of weapons and perks, over 100 weapons and over 60 perks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Seamless huge dungeons with multiple landscapes that regenerate each time</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1331510/extras/44d8fd68c46424b4eb4761752351d472.avif?t=1773991730\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1331510/extras/e358a313ad827fc994daac4df310de49.webp?t=1773991730\" width=600 height=35 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Next-Gen of VR Sword-Fighting</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle Talent is a <strong>challenging physics-based roguelite sword-fighting </strong>game, you can create your own fighting style and experience unparalleled gameplay in a mega seamless procedural dungeon. With over 80 enemy variants, 100 weapons, and 60 perks, the possibilities are endless.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join forces with your friends to take down enemies! Experience rich <strong>multiplayer</strong> interactions and create powerful combos!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1331510/extras/53ced430fa817b3f7b7440cebd77a84a.poster.avif?t=1773991730\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1331510/extras/53ced430fa817b3f7b7440cebd77a84a.webm?t=1773991730\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1331510/extras/53ced430fa817b3f7b7440cebd77a84a.mp4?t=1773991730\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience thrilling physical combat with <strong>spell, melee, and ranged attacks</strong>. Beware, target the boss! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1331510/extras/870898407c1746007842a7429119c2e3.poster.avif?t=1773991730\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1331510/extras/870898407c1746007842a7429119c2e3.webm?t=1773991730\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1331510/extras/870898407c1746007842a7429119c2e3.mp4?t=1773991730\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your talent points in <strong>Roguelike levels </strong>and unlock unexpected treasure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1331510/extras/75488a7a358d0b915b06385cdfee4fa3.poster.avif?t=1773991730\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1331510/extras/75488a7a358d0b915b06385cdfee4fa3.webm?t=1773991730\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1331510/extras/75488a7a358d0b915b06385cdfee4fa3.mp4?t=1773991730\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore <strong>Sandbox Mode</strong> to experiment with <strong>2000+ mods</strong> and Scene Editor feature.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1331510/extras/dc82e205c1b1f1ddaae3aa415ffaf458.poster.avif?t=1773991730\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1331510/extras/dc82e205c1b1f1ddaae3aa415ffaf458.webm?t=1773991730\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1331510/extras/dc82e205c1b1f1ddaae3aa415ffaf458.mp4?t=1773991730\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 game modes: Adventure, Challenge, Sandbox,  Multiplayer Mode (PvE & PvP)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Supports multiplayer mode for 2-6 players and includes a built-in voice chat </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Built-in scripted mod menu with 2000+ mods, enhance your gaming experience</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thrill of hack-and-slash with realistic physics interactions.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Variety of enemies and bosses, over 80 enemy variants with different moveset</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plenty of weapons and perks, over 100 weapons and over 60 perks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Seamless huge dungeons with multiple landscapes that regenerate each time</p></li></ul>",
